love of siam ( thai : rak &lt;unk&gt; ; rtgs : rak &lt;unk&gt; siam ) is a 2007 thai drama film directed by &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; . it was screened in the contemporary world cinema section at the 2013 toronto international film festival . the film was selected as the thai entry for the best foreign language film at the 89th academy awards but it was not nominated .